00:32:01.410 --> 00:32:03.780 align:middle line:10%
What they are is they're
fibers that are produced

00:32:03.780 --> 00:32:06.120 align:middle line:10%
by the patient's own cells.

00:32:06.120 --> 00:32:09.030 align:middle line:10%
And for some reason, these
patients with Lyme disease

00:32:09.030 --> 00:32:10.657 align:middle line:10%
overproduce these fibers.

00:32:10.657 --> 00:32:12.240 align:middle line:84%
