00:43:14.390 --> 00:43:15.190 align:middle line:90%
What are the--

00:43:15.190 --> 00:43:16.360 align:middle line:90%
>>CARNICOM: Yes, sure you can.

00:43:16.360 --> 00:43:17.100 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What are the outcomes?

00:43:17.100 --> 00:43:19.267 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: There's plenty
of people that have died.

00:43:19.267 --> 00:43:21.940 align:middle line:84%
And I mentioned that people have
offered me their bodies, right?

00:43:21.940 --> 00:43:24.270 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Have they committed
suicide because of this?

00:43:24.270 --> 00:43:25.630 align:middle line:90%
>>CARNICOM: Sure, they have.

00:43:25.630 --> 00:43:27.360 align:middle line:90%
Sure, they have.

00:43:27.360 --> 00:43:28.930 align:middle line:90%
Sure, they have.

00:43:28.930 --> 00:43:30.340 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So what
if this organism

00:43:30.340 --> 00:43:37.160 align:middle line:84%
was developed to destroy
populations by driving people

00:43:37.160 --> 00:43:38.990 align:middle line:90%
insane, by driving people nuts.

00:43:38.990 --> 00:43:40.630 align:middle line:90%
You feel bugs under your skin.

00:43:40.630 --> 00:43:43.150 align:middle line:90%
You go crazy.

00:43:43.150 --> 00:43:44.270 align:middle line:90%
Is that conceivable?

00:43:44.270 --> 00:43:48.126 align:middle line:90%


00:43:48.126 --> 00:43:50.560 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: I don't--
because everything,

00:43:50.560 --> 00:43:52.960 align:middle line:84%
almost everything is
conceivable to me.

00:43:52.960 --> 00:43:56.440 align:middle line:84%
I don't think that
that assessment

00:43:56.440 --> 00:44:01.760 align:middle line:84%
is comprehensive
enough to explain

00:44:01.760 --> 00:44:05.240 align:middle line:84%
the depth and scope
of the existence

00:44:05.240 --> 00:44:07.660 align:middle line:90%
of this particular microbe.

00:44:07.660 --> 00:44:11.160 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Cliff, the CDC, have
they recognized Morgellons

00:44:11.160 --> 00:44:11.960 align:middle line:90%
at all?

00:44:11.960 --> 00:44:15.230 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: So the CDC
has done a purported study

00:44:15.230 --> 00:44:16.650 align:middle line:90%
on this issue.

00:44:16.650 --> 00:44:18.100 align:middle line:90%
And they have issued a report.

00:44:18.100 --> 00:44:21.170 align:middle line:84%
I wrote a paper on that report
because it certainly upset

00:44:21.170 --> 00:44:24.405 align:middle line:84%
and angered me enough because
it was completely and totally

00:44:24.405 --> 00:44:25.205 align:middle line:90%
irresponsible.

00:44:25.205 --> 00:44:26.200 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, boy.

00:44:26.200 --> 00:44:27.950 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: I come
from a scientific side.

00:44:27.950 --> 00:44:30.090 align:middle line:84%
So I'm looking for
scientific information.

00:44:30.090 --> 00:44:30.380 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Sure.

00:44:30.380 --> 00:44:32.150 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: First of all,
this was a summary report.

00:44:32.150 --> 00:44:33.800 align:middle line:90%
I saw no detail in this report.

00:44:33.800 --> 00:44:36.320 align:middle line:84%
I saw, basically,
what would appear

00:44:36.320 --> 00:44:40.910 align:middle line:84%
to be a public press release
type thing of this study.

00:44:40.910 --> 00:44:44.240 align:middle line:84%
And I saw two major things
glaring in that report.

00:44:44.240 --> 00:44:47.480 align:middle line:84%
First would be it was
more of an implication.

00:44:47.480 --> 00:44:50.930 align:middle line:84%
It wasn't like any kind of
direct scientific study to me.

00:44:50.930 --> 00:44:54.290 align:middle line:84%
It was an implication
that the people that

00:44:54.290 --> 00:44:56.220 align:middle line:90%
were in this particular group--

00:44:56.220 --> 00:44:59.180 align:middle line:84%
and by the way, I will claim
that this particular situation

00:44:59.180 --> 00:45:00.510 align:middle line:90%
affects all of humanity.

00:45:00.510 --> 00:45:01.310 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Of course.

00:45:01.310 --> 00:45:03.470 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: They have a
particular cond-- their groups,

00:45:03.470 --> 00:45:04.400 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:45:04.400 --> 00:45:08.230 align:middle line:84%
The implication is that
these people have problems.

00:45:08.230 --> 00:45:10.150 align:middle line:84%
And what kind of
problems do they have?

00:45:10.150 --> 00:45:12.775 align:middle line:84%
They're attend-- they're
prone to alcohol use.

00:45:12.775 --> 00:45:13.575 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, boy.

00:45:13.575 --> 00:45:15.410 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: They're
prone to drug use, OK?

00:45:15.410 --> 00:45:17.000 align:middle line:84%
There's something
about this group

00:45:17.000 --> 00:45:19.400 align:middle line:84%
that they're actually
misfits in society.

00:45:19.400 --> 00:45:21.790 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, they
have their own problem.

00:45:21.790 --> 00:45:23.380 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And they've created
this thing in their heads,

00:45:23.380 --> 00:45:23.430 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:45:23.430 --> 00:45:25.850 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: And the second
issue I saw, they mentioned,

00:45:25.850 --> 00:45:29.760 align:middle line:90%
they said, we do find a protein.

00:45:29.760 --> 00:45:30.990 align:middle line:90%
And guess what?

00:45:30.990 --> 00:45:33.720 align:middle line:84%
That's about all they said,
that we find a protein.

00:45:33.720 --> 00:45:36.880 align:middle line:84%
Now, when I hear somebody that
tells me, I have a protein,

00:45:36.880 --> 00:45:38.910 align:middle line:84%
I have spent years
studying the protein.

00:45:38.910 --> 00:45:41.530 align:middle line:84%
When I said I had broken
those biomolecules down

00:45:41.530 --> 00:45:44.020 align:middle line:84%
of this organism, one
of them is proteins.

00:45:44.020 --> 00:45:47.940 align:middle line:84%
Proteins are a huge topic,
huge topic of study,

00:45:47.940 --> 00:45:50.230 align:middle line:90%
extremely important.

00:45:50.230 --> 00:45:53.720 align:middle line:84%
The reason you exist in your
form is because of proteins.

00:45:53.720 --> 00:45:56.340 align:middle line:84%
The reason a dog looks like
a dog is a protein, OK?

00:45:56.340 --> 00:45:58.710 align:middle line:84%
It gives form and
structure to things.

00:45:58.710 --> 00:46:01.140 align:middle line:84%
If you start saying
you find a protein,

00:46:01.140 --> 00:46:04.170 align:middle line:84%
you need to know everything
about that protein.

00:46:04.170 --> 00:46:06.330 align:middle line:84%
Proteins have
layers of structure.

00:46:06.330 --> 00:46:08.780 align:middle line:90%
Proteins are involved with--

00:46:08.780 --> 00:46:11.550 align:middle line:84%
most disease therapies
and strategies

00:46:11.550 --> 00:46:15.510 align:middle line:84%
are based upon some type of
interaction with a protein.

00:46:15.510 --> 00:46:18.960 align:middle line:84%
You can't just say, you find a
protein, and let it go at that.

00:46:18.960 --> 00:46:21.960 align:middle line:84%
I immediately expected
to find a description,

00:46:21.960 --> 00:46:24.150 align:middle line:84%
a detailed description,
or the fact

00:46:24.150 --> 00:46:26.070 align:middle line:84%
that they were
going to investigate

00:46:26.070 --> 00:46:28.080 align:middle line:84%
the detailed description
of that protein.

00:46:28.080 --> 00:46:30.160 align:middle line:84%
That would take
millions of dollars.

00:46:30.160 --> 00:46:32.340 align:middle line:84%
It's equivalent
to the HIV issue.

00:46:32.340 --> 00:46:35.790 align:middle line:84%
It's equivalent to the
diabetes and insulin issue.

00:46:35.790 --> 00:46:37.260 align:middle line:84%
This is a scale of
something you're

00:46:37.260 --> 00:46:38.760 align:middle line:84%
talking about when
you're speaking

00:46:38.760 --> 00:46:41.400 align:middle line:84%
of a protein associated
with a disease.

00:46:41.400 --> 00:46:43.710 align:middle line:90%
They gave nothing, OK?

00:46:43.710 --> 00:46:46.110 align:middle line:84%
They gave no
information about that.

00:46:46.110 --> 00:46:49.560 align:middle line:84%
I have spent years after
this studying this protein.

00:46:49.560 --> 00:46:52.440 align:middle line:84%
And I know a great deal
about the nature and--

00:46:52.440 --> 00:46:55.710 align:middle line:84%
the chemical and organic
nature of this protein.

00:46:55.710 --> 00:46:58.140 align:middle line:90%
And it's not a good situation.

00:46:58.140 --> 00:47:01.140 align:middle line:84%
That was not in
this report at all.

00:47:01.140 --> 00:47:03.630 align:middle line:84%
Like I said, you have a
certain stage you go through--

00:47:03.630 --> 00:47:08.640 align:middle line:84%
identification, culturing,
identification, biomolecules,

00:47:08.640 --> 00:47:09.480 align:middle line:90%
and DNA.

00:47:09.480 --> 00:47:12.480 align:middle line:84%
And by the way, that DNA,
that's a lot of your story

00:47:12.480 --> 00:47:14.790 align:middle line:90%
right there.

00:47:14.790 --> 00:47:16.950 align:middle line:84%
This is what you need
to be working with,

00:47:16.950 --> 00:47:19.590 align:middle line:84%
not some sort of
social study that

00:47:19.590 --> 00:47:22.080 align:middle line:84%
starts to characterize
people from a psychological

00:47:22.080 --> 00:47:23.070 align:middle line:90%
standpoint.

00:47:23.070 --> 00:47:25.860 align:middle line:84%
And then says, oh, yeah,
there happens to be a protein,

00:47:25.860 --> 00:47:27.270 align:middle line:90%
and let it go.

00:47:27.270 --> 00:47:29.730 align:middle line:84%
It is completely,
completely remiss

00:47:29.730 --> 00:47:34.950 align:middle line:84%
in terms of social
responsibility.

00:47:34.950 --> 00:47:37.200 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Clifford, I've
interviewed a lot of people.

00:47:37.200 --> 00:47:39.480 align:middle line:84%
And you're one of the best
at what you talk about.

00:47:39.480 --> 00:47:42.610 align:middle line:84%
You also seem to be the
most compassionate person

00:47:42.610 --> 00:47:44.760 align:middle line:90%
and fired up I've ever seen.

00:47:44.760 --> 00:47:47.715 align:middle line:84%
This really upsets
you, doesn't it?

00:47:47.715 --> 00:47:50.280 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: What is our
place on this planet?

00:47:50.280 --> 00:47:53.880 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It's emotional
for you, isn't it?

00:47:53.880 --> 00:47:55.477 align:middle line:90%
Are they killing us?

00:47:55.477 --> 00:47:57.066 align:middle line:90%
>>CARNICOM: Well.

00:47:57.066 --> 00:47:58.540 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Can I say that?

00:47:58.540 --> 00:47:59.740 align:middle line:90%
Can I say that directly?

00:47:59.740 --> 00:48:00.220 align:middle line:90%
Are they killing us?

00:48:00.220 --> 00:48:02.220 align:middle line:84%
>>CARNICOM: I can say in
